Lucas, a rescued #FlyingFox boy is enjoying an all time favourite ğŸŒ while having some of the bothersome #batflie parasites picked out of his fur. Batflies are a special kind of wingless flies found on flying foxes and microbats. Although there is no evidence of them doing any harm, their number usually reflects how well the animal is doing.
